body.name: Florida Keys
body.description: Florida Keys custom map highlighting each of the keys, including Key West, Sugarloaf Key, Big Pine Key, Marathon, Islamorada, Plantation Key and Key Largo. Sites include Southernmost Point USA, Sparky’s Landing, Dolphin Research Center, Robbie’s, Seven Mile Bridge, and John Pennekamp Coral Reef State Park.
